OL,3,CMurder charge after man, 24, dies in
OL,4,Cvillage
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of a 24-year-old
OL,8,Fin a Somerset village.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to an
OL,11,Faddress in Coronation Close, Ruishton
OL,12,Fat around 8pm on Monday 19 February to
OL,13,Fa report of a man with serious
OL,14,Finjuries.
OL,16,FJordan Simcock, 24, was taken to
OL,17,FSouthmead Hospital and died on the
OL,18,Fafternoon of Wednesday 21 February.
OL,20,FHis family is being supported by
OL,21,Fspecially-trained police officers.
