OL,3,CMurder charge after man, 24, dies in
OL,4,Cvillage
OL,6,FA forensic post-mortem examination and
OL,7,Fformal identification are due to be
OL,8,Fcompleted in the coming days.
OL,10,FMichael Drake, 46, from Taunton, was
OL,11,Fcharged with one count of murder
OL,12,Fovernight and appeared before Taunton
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on the morning of
OL,14,FThursday 22 February.
OL,16,FHe was remanded into custody to appear
OL,17,Fat Bristol Crown Court on Friday 23
OL,18,FFebruary.
