OL,3,CMurder charge after man, 24, dies in
OL,4,Cvillage
OL,6,FA second man, also in his 40s, who was
OL,7,Farrested earlier this week, has been
OL,8,Freleased with no further action.
OL,10,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Simon
OL,12,FDewfall, said: "I'd like to reassure
OL,13,Feveryone that we believe this to be an
OL,14,Fisolated incident involving people who
OL,15,Fwere known to each other and that
OL,16,Fthere is no wider risk to the public.
